data.description: Beautiful 4 BR 2 BA single family home built in 2020 This home is only 3 years old. You first arrive to a large driveway and a 2-car garage. As soon as you walk in you have a private bedroom to your right which can also be used as an office. A laundry room to your left and you walk into the spacious kitchen with plenty of counter space a kitchen island overlooking your living room. A great place to spend some quality family time. There are 2 more bedrooms and a master bedroom with a walk-in shower and dual vanity sinks. Very little lawn maintenance is required for this home. Come check this gem out for yourself.
